{"tid":1682474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重開！理大畢業V煞快閃活動","createTime":"2019-10-30T05:25:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T07:09:38.000Z","uid":322788,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4319d1f39862dada46ab2938e010abb282508116","tid":1682474,"uid":322788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T05:25:37.000Z","msg":"今日下晝兩點半同七點半係草can隔離百步梯有活動啊！！<br />\n<br />\n首先我地會一齊影一張V煞嘅合照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後再係學校入面小型遊行(3點起步)<br />\n遊行路線：百步梯 - 民主牆 - m core 讀宣言、唱榮光<br />\n我要滕錦光知道理大人唔係廢既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎咁多位畢業生、埋大手足、其他手足一齊撐場！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位爭氣啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n溫馨小提示：<br />\n1. 參加嘅手足儘量畢業袍/blackbloc<br />\n2. 自備面具，無嘅戴口罩/自行矇面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/62hyCO7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F62hyCO7.jpg&h=3110bf2f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Ace6Ht.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Ace6Ht.jpg&h=c881f0ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FQ2R8VP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFQ2R8VP.jpg&h=cf5323e3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Th5oZ2u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTh5o